name: Pixel Decomposition of the HeN Logo
description:
"Adobe Illustrator vector file, post-processed in Photoshop. Faux pixel noise entirely generated with downscaled iteractions of the Hic et Nunc logo and the phrases ""here and now"" and ""aqui e agora"". Originally released on 22 May 2021 as HeN OBJKT 93321. New release with higher resolution.
"
